{"type":null,"faqId":14021,"title":"为什么别的蓝牙设备无法检测到我的蓝牙？","answer":"<p>\n  <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">可能有以下原因：</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">未开启蓝牙可检测性。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <a name=\"gen-id1.8.8.2.2.1.1\"></a><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">您可以在蓝牙设置界面，点击荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的蓝牙名称，使您的荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">可以被别的设备检测到。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <a name=\"figd0e2734\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.8.8.2.2.1.2.1\"></a><span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44740\" width=\"529\" height=\"476\" alt=\"\" /></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span>&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">蓝牙可检测性超时。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <a name=\"gen-id1.8.8.2.2.2.1\"></a><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">您可以在蓝牙设置界面，点击</span> <a name=\"gen-id1.8.8.2.2.2.1.1.1.1\"></a><b><span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44741\" width=\"29\" height=\"21\" alt=\"\" /></span></b><span>&nbsp;&gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">检测超时设置</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，点击选择蓝牙可被检测到的时长并同时开启可检测性。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <a name=\"figd0e2749\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.8.8.2.2.2.2.1\"></a><span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44742\" width=\"529\" height=\"476\" alt=\"\" /></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span>&nbsp;</span>\n</p>","faqTypeId":170,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5681","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Internet-Data-Sharing","isTop":"